commit.message: Add working emotion analysis capture code
More subtle improvements to the AI

Add njobs=1 to pm.sample call

Some systems enable multiprocessing, which unexpectedly changes the
sample size.
Add automatic entries to player.dat if player is not found
Make bot self-aware without needing a UUID
Playing with changes to the final formula
Bring everything together and have AI actually make decisions
Add caching of player data that gets loaded every game
Add bluffing heuristic to the action model
Add confidence estimation for opposing players
Removed extra text from emotion analysis that linked to image display
